This is a plugin for IntelliJ to convert source code into html with all formatting and highlighting.<br/>
WARNING: this plugin is out of date, it will only work IntelliJ 10 (and may be earlier versions)

This is and import of this project on google code https://code.google.com/p/htmlexport/

If you just want to convert code into html please consider trying "Copy as HTML" plugin (http://plugins.intellij.net/plugin/?idea&pluginId=190)